## CHANGELOG.md

```markdown
# Changelog

All notable changes to the Game Tribe project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2025-05-14

### Added

#### Core Features
User Authentication System
  - User registration with email and password
  - Secure login/logout functionality
  - JWT token-based authentication
  - Password hashing with bcrypt

Game Catalog
  - Home page with game grid display
  - Featured games carousel
  - Game details modal
  - Genre-based categorization

Shopping Cart
  - Add/remove items from cart
  - Quantity adjustment
  - Cart persistence in localStorage
  - Real-time total calculation with tax

Checkout System
  - Shipping information form
  - Order summary
  - Order confirmation modal
  - Order number generation

User Profile
  - Customizable avatar (8 options)
  - Personal information display
  - Editable personal note
  - Member statistics

### Community Features
Favorites System
  - Add/remove games from favorites
  - Quick favorite toggle on game cards
  - Favorites display in profile
  - Heart icon visual feedback

### Admin Features
Admin Dashboard
  - Total users, orders, games statistics
  - Revenue tracking
  - Recent orders display
  - Quick navigation to admin sections

User Management
  - View all users
  - Search users by name/email
  - Toggle admin privileges
  - Delete user accounts
  - View user order counts

Order Management
  - View all orders
  - Filter by status
  - Update order status
  - View detailed order information
  - Color-coded status badges

### Technical Features
Frontend Architecture
  - React 18 with functional components
  - React Router v6 for navigation
  - Context API for state management
  - Centralized API service
  - Responsive design

Backend Architecture
  - Express.js REST API
  - MongoDB with Mongoose ODM
  - JWT middleware for auth
  - Admin authorization middleware
  - CORS configuration

Security
  - Protected routes
  - Input validation
  - Error handling
  - Environment variables
  - Secure password storage

### UI/UX Features
- Custom CSS with CSS variables
- Bootstrap 5 integration
- Font Awesome icons
- Loading states
- Error messages
- Hover effects and transitions
- Mobile-responsive design

### Development Tools
- ESLint configuration
- Proxy setup for development
- Admin creation script
- Folder structure organization

### Fixed
- Authentication redirect loops
- MongoDB population issues
- Order status update bugs
- Image fallback handling
- Cart persistence issues

### Security
- Added JWT token expiration
- Implemented admin route protection
- Added input sanitization
- Secured API endpoints
- Environment variable usage

### Added
- Initial project setup
- Basic authentication flow
- Game catalog implementation
- Shopping cart functionality
- User profile pages
---

## Future Releases 

### [1.1.0] - TBD
- Payment gateway integration
- Email notifications
- Advanced search filters
- User messaging system
- Social login options
- Game recommendations
- Wishlist feature
- Performance optimizations